2026-06-04 12:31:43,642 | DEBUG    |   ## Root cause
2026-06-04 12:31:43,642 | DEBUG    |   The current `gin.Context.Keys` field is typed as `map[string]any`, limiting keys to `string` types. The issue requests refactoring this to `map[any]any` to support arbitrary comparable types as keys, as demonstrated in the example code (`ctx.Set(111, "111")`, `ctx.Get(key{})`).
